</br>1 The word that occurred to Jeremiah from Jehovah, when Neb·u·chad·rez´zar the king of Babylon and all his military force and all the kingdoms of the earth, the dominion under his hand, and all the peoples were fighting against Jerusalem and against all her cities, saying:
